<p>For the author:</p>
<p>-I&#8217;ve always heard &#8220;breve&#8221; pronounced &#8220;breh-veh&#8221; or &#8220;breh-vey,&#8221; depending on American accents.  Never before &#8220;breev.&#8221;</p>
