<li class="comment" id="comment-52671">
    <div class="authorpic">
		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536?s=80' class='avatar avatar-80 photo avatar-default' height='80' width='80' /> 
	</div>
    <div class="entry">

        <h3>Livia <span class="date">Aug 27th, 2007</span></h3>
        <p>Cappuccino doesn&#8217;t mean little mountain in Italian, Italian for little mountain is &#8220;collina&#8221;, like the soccer referee</p>
