        <h3>Leonardo <span class="date">Aug 27th, 2007</span></h3>
        <p>I like your  post, very informative and great illustrations, but I must say:<br />
Are you out of your mind?</p>
<p>Your Macchiato shows something like a mini cappuccino.  To make a macchiato you put a teaspoon or two of milk, no more. It&#8217;s not a 1:1 relationship of ezpreso to milk, NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!</p>
<p>Also, there&#8217;s macchiato caldo, e macchiato freddo.<br />
In macchiato caldo steam milk is used, in macchiato freddo cold milk is used.</p>
<p>Mamma mia!</p>
