        <h3>Andreas <span class="date">Aug 28th, 2007</span></h3>
        <p>A note on the breve pronunciation.  In English breve is &#8220;breev&#8221;, but in the world of coffee, one pronounces the final e just as in latte, so &#8220;brev-ay&#8221; would be the better caption for that drink.</p>
