<li class="comment" id="comment-52766">
    <div class="authorpic">
		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e1faaa1afae08c86d7378141f17b26a3?s=80&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D80&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /> 
	</div>
    <div class="entry">

        <h3>jhonny_paradox <span class="date">Aug 29th, 2007</span></h3>
        <p>A suggestion to quell the international coffee connoisseurs: create a &#8220;Coffees of the World&#8221; diagram chart with different examples of the various coffee beverages around the world.</p>
<p>The only problem with this is getting a majority to agree on what is what.</p>
