        <h3><a href='http://43kg.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Adam</a> <span class="date">Apr 19th, 2008</span></h3>
        <p>The ‘flat white’ should be called ‘cafe con leche’ the standard spanish coffee.<br />
You get a big cup with some espresso in it placed in front of you and then the steamed milk is poured on top. You can decide how much milk you want, great.</p>
