        <h3>sergio <span class="date">Jun 25th, 2008</span></h3>
        <p>A Cappucino is so named because when made properly with a brown rim of crema around the outer part of the cup and the white foam in the middle, it looks like the top of a Capuchin monks head. Not because it is the same colour as a Capuchin monks robe!</p>
		<div class="actions">
