    <div class="entry">

        <h3>Stu <span class="date">Jan 4th, 2009</span></h3>
        <p>So, why are Starbucks going so badly wrong when you ask for a caramel macchiato? Caramel aside, it&#8217;s just another Latte isn&#8217;t it? Don&#8217;t get my wrong &#8211; I like Starbucks, but it&#8217;s American coffee flavoured drink. Here in the UK, Costa is far better for coffee.</p>
<p>Top work &#8211; keep it up!</p>
