        <h3><a href='http://alfou@broadpark.no' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>another version</a> <span class="date">Dec 2nd, 2009</span></h3>
        <p>I made this one (but I haven&#8217;t &#8220;published&#8221; it anywhere, and it&#8217;s based on yours):</p>
<p><a href="http://folk.ntnu.no/anderfo/pics/temp/nyheter/espressodrinks.png" rel="nofollow">http://folk.ntnu.no/anderfo/pics/temp/nyheter/espressodrinks.png</a></p>
