- I changed the coffee cup sizes to fit with the amount of liquids.<br />
- I haven&#8217;t added these yet but might do it:<br />
* Caffè corretto (italian)<br />
* Café au lait (french)<br />
* Cortado (spanish)<br />
* Caffè ristretto (italian)<br />
* Latte macchiato (italian)</p>
