        <h3><a href='http://www.dietsolutionreviewscam.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Diet Solution</a> <span class="date">Oct 31st, 2010</span></h3>
        <p>The Diet Solution is a program created by nutritionist and trainer Isabel De Los Rios which claims to allow you to lose weight without counting calories. </p>
<p>This is done by individualizing the nutrition plan to the specific needs of your body through a process known as ?etabolic Typing.? Through this process The Diet Solution shows you the specific foods and portions your body needs for optimal health and weight loss.</p>
